\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch \f1\fs24\b1\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Stranger is to be allowed access to the town for half a year to study and observe the town's people. Discretion must be exercised. Stranger to be billeted in the dead lecturer's room at the expense of Building 4's commune tin for the duration of his stay; however, the rights of Ancient Lights and Wake Of The Room shall be null and void in his case, should they be requested. Food and spiritual sustenance to be provided by the Town Hall. The plans for a small welcome celebration, in order to showcase the hospitality of our valley, are being finalised, with funds coming from the Mayor's personal finances. }
